1)COMMIT:
++++++++
IT IS USED TO SAVE THE TRANSACTIONS LIKE (INSERT,UPDATE,DELETE)

BUT SNOWFLAKE IS AUTO COMMIT NO NEED TO USE COMMIT.
AUTOMATICALLY IT PERFORM COMMIT.

TO CHECK THAT:
-------------
SHOW PARAMETERS LIKE 'AUTOCOMMIT' IN SESSION;

ROLLBACK WILL NOT WORK BECAOUSE ITS AUTO COMMI.

TO MODIFY:
----------
ALTER SESSION SET AUTOCOMMIT = TRUE;(IF IT IS TRUE THEN WE CANNOT ROLLBACK IT WONT WORK)
ALTER SESSION SET AUTOCOMMIT = FALSE;(IF IT IS FALSE THEN U CAN ROLLBACK)
SO ROLLBACK IS RECOMMENDED ONLY IF AUTO COMMIT IS FALSE.    <------



2)ROLLBACK
ALTER SESSION SET AUTOCOMMIT = FALSE;

NOW UCAN INSERT DATA U CAN ROLLBACK IT WORKS.

